    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are truly a formidable foe and this emanates with every step you take. All hostile creatures who would enter within or start their turn within 30 feet of you must make a Constutition saving throw against your Taijutsu Save DC. On a failed save they suffer a -1 penalty to their AC, Saving throws, and attack rolls. A creature only makes this save once per round and may make a saving throw at the end of their turn to end the effect.</p>",
